    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Escape from Hadrian’s Wall, where history and destiny collide!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 402 A. D. Britannia, the waning years of the Roman Empire. Delve into the depths in this VR puzzle adventure as a nameless prisoner held in the fortress of Hadrian’s Wall. A chance encounter offers salvation and peril alike as you come to the aid of a mother and her infant son, whose fates are entwined with destiny.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on the mantle of witch’s apprentice, guided by your mystical mentor. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105560/extras/f47ab71818b6358a416104ef0df0e2e5.poster.avif?t=1762807857\" aria-label=\"The player&#039;s hand pours elixir into a scrying bowl, which erupts in pink fire and smoke.\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105560/extras/f47ab71818b6358a416104ef0df0e2e5.webm?t=1762807857\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105560/extras/f47ab71818b6358a416104ef0df0e2e5.mp4?t=1762807857\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Exercise your intellect and wield magical artifacts to solve intricate puzzles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105560/extras/1a6bb8730958810a762a9d1aa066c9f0.poster.avif?t=1762807857\" aria-label=\"The player&#039;s hand holds an elemental wand, shooting fire balls to ignite torches on the wall. A door magically opens.\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105560/extras/1a6bb8730958810a762a9d1aa066c9f0.webm?t=1762807857\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105560/extras/1a6bb8730958810a762a9d1aa066c9f0.mp4?t=1762807857\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cast magical cards to dispel elemental golems.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105560/extras/a82b1dc7332ec0120daa6d98f251559d.poster.avif?t=1762807857\" aria-label=\"The player&#039;s hand plays a spell card and constructs a Fire Golem on the playing field.\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105560/extras/a82b1dc7332ec0120daa6d98f251559d.webm?t=1762807857\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105560/extras/a82b1dc7332ec0120daa6d98f251559d.mp4?t=1762807857\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Navigate the labyrinthine fortress beneath the wall, uncovering ancient secrets best left undisturbed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105560/extras/6eb31a3768d9d2c415184df84ad292e9.poster.avif?t=1762807857\" aria-label=\"A wall splits and separates, revealing a hidden passageway.\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105560/extras/6eb31a3768d9d2c415184df84ad292e9.webm?t=1762807857\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105560/extras/6eb31a3768d9d2c415184df84ad292e9.mp4?t=1762807857\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The time of destiny has come. It sits on a razor’s edge. Now, you wield the blade. </p>",
